  "response": "In the movie **\"Percy Jackson & the Olympians: The Lightning Thief\"** (2010), Percy Jackson is portrayed as a **12-year-old** demigod. This age aligns with the character's age in the original book series by Rick Riordan, where Percy begins his adventures as a young teenager discovering his divine heritage and embarking on quests related to Greek mythology.\n\nThe actor **Logan Lerman**, who plays Percy, was around 18 years old at the time of filming, but the character himself is depicted as being 12 years old in the story.\n\nIt's worth noting that as the film series progresses, Percy's age may advance to reflect his development and the progression of the storyline. However, in the first movie, he is specifically 12 years old.",
